== Example for Apache conf

  <VirtualHost *:80>
    ServerName *.clockingit.com
    DocumentRoot /path/application/public/
    ErrorLog /path/application/log/server.log

    <Directory /path/application/public/>
      Options ExecCGI FollowSymLinks
      AllowOverride all
      Allow from all
      Order allow,deny
    </Directory>
  </VirtualHost>

